      • FBPage

        public FBPage(facebook4j.Facebook facebookIn,
              String username)
       throws ClassNotFoundException,
              javax.servlet.ServletException,
              IOException,
              SQLException,
              facebook4j.FacebookException,
              facebook4j.internal.org.json.JSONException
        This constructor is used so you don't have to make an API call to Facebook. That way you won't consume unnecesary calls
        Parameters:
        facebookIn - Facebook Object of the user
        username - User, that way you can directly go to DB and get the PageId
        Throws:
        ClassNotFoundException - ok
        javax.servlet.ServletException - ok
        IOException - ok
        SQLException - ok
        facebook4j.FacebookException - ok
        facebook4j.internal.org.json.JSONException - ok
